            <h5>ATM Interface (E-Pass)</h5>
            <p>An in-person machine that takes cash and stores credit for prepaid highway toll fees. The interface runs on Webkit, the reason being the client wants to be able to update the system remotely without technicians on the field.</p>
            <p>There are about a handful of unique views, and the user interaction is simple (touch, single-tap only) because of the hardware limitations. I used <u>plain JavaScript</u> and <u>CSS animations</u> triggered by attributes. </p>

