            <h5>Quart</h5>
            <p>A hosted markdown blogging platform and web-based text editor.</p>
            <p>I used <u>Backbone Routers, Views, and Models</u> here. The text editor is a personally extended <u>Ace Editor</u>. The parts of speech highlighting and writing assistant is coded in by hand, tagging aided by a <a href="https://github.com/singingfish/jspos">POS library</a>. Templating is powered by <u>Underscore</u>.</p>
            <img src="http://placehold.it/970x200" alt="">
            <p><b>Status: Shelved</b>, the user base was small (80), and the cost to sustain was too much for a free app. I decided to make a similar service that was much more sustainable.</p>
